#######################################
# gmail mailbox #
#######################################
IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User toluwani.adesegha@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass google | grep app-pswd | cut -d ' ' -f 2"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile ~/tools/mutt/certificates/imap.gmail.com.pem
AuthMech PLAIN

# Remote storage
IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

# Local storage
MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/mail/gmail/inbox
Flatten .

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns *
CopyArrivalDate yes
Create Near


