# outlook mailbox #
#######################################
IMAPAccount outlook
Host outlook.office365.com
User tolu@adesegha.ca
PassCmd "pass microsoft | grep app-pswd | cut -d ' ' -f 2"
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersion TLSv1.2
CertificateFile ~/tools/mutt/certificates/outlook.office365.com.pem
AuthMechs PLAIN

# Remote storage
IMAPStore outlook-remote
Account outlook

# Local storage
MaildirStore outlook-local
Path ~/mail/outlook/
Inbox ~/mail/outlook/inbox
Flatten .

Channel outlook
Far :outlook-remote:
Near :outlook-local:
Patterns *
CopyArrivalDate yes
Create Both
Expunge Both
Sync All
SyncState *


